HEADWORD: Dedition
<hw>De*di"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>deditio</ets>, fr. <ets>dedere</ets> to give away, surrender;
<ets>de-</ets> + <ets>dare</ets> to give.]</ety> <def>The act of
yielding; surrender.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir M.
Hale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
